'''Epiphany''' is  simple, fast Webkit web browser for [[GNOME]].

== Installation ==

=== USE flags ===

{{USEflag|package=www-client/epiphany}}

=== Emerge ===

{{Emerge|www-client/epiphany}}

=== Additional software ===

For Flash support install {{Package|www-plugins/adobe-flash}} and {{Package|www-plugins/nspluginwrapper}}:

{{Emerge|adobe-flash nspluginwrapper}}
 
Execute the following command to get flash working in Epiphany:

{{RootCmd|/usr/lib/nspluginwrapper/*/linux/npconfig -v -a -n -i}}

